sumptions on the coverings.\n  We illustrate the resulting theory by applications to $\\alpha$-modulation and\nBesov spaces. All known embedding results for these spaces are special cases of\nour approach; often, we improve considerably upon the state of the art.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 31 May 2016 16:36:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 15 Feb 2018 13:05:24 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 5 Oct 2019 17:40:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-08"}
