 by model calculations including substantial elastic interactions\nof heavy quarks with an expanding strongly-interacting medium.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Jun 2016 15:07:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 3 Nov 2016 19:59:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-04"}
